solution:
若入射中子打到晶体上产生衍射，则入射波长也约为 \(10^{-10} \mathrm{~m}\)，因此入射中子的能量为

\[
\begin{aligned}
E & = \frac{p^{2}}{2 m_{\mathrm{n}}} = \frac{\left(\frac{h}{\lambda}\right)^{2}}{2 m_{\mathrm{n}}} = \frac{h^{2}}{2 m_{\mathrm{n}} \lambda^{2}} = \left(\frac{h c}{\lambda}\right)^{2} \cdot \frac{1}{m_{\mathrm{n}} c^{2}} \\
& = \left(\frac{4.1358 \times 10^{-15} \times 3 \times 10^{8}}{1 \times 10^{-10}}\right)^{2} \cdot \frac{1}{939 \times 10^{6} \, \mathrm{eV}} \\
& = 8.2 \times 10^{-2} \, \mathrm{(eV)}
\end{aligned}
\]

铜中自由电子浓度
\[
n=\frac{8.9 \times 10^3}{63.5} \times 6.02 \times 10^{23}=8.4 \times 10^{28} \, \mathrm{m}^{-3}
\]

费米能
\[
\begin{aligned}
E_{\mathrm{F}}^{0} & =\frac{\hbar^2}{2m} \left(3\pi^{2}n\right)^{\frac{2}{3}} =\frac{\left(1.055 \times 10^{-34}\right)^{2}}{2 \times 9.1 \times 10^{-31}} \times \left(3\pi^{2} \times 8.4 \times 10^{28}\right)^{\frac{2}{3}} \\
& =1.12 \times 10^{-18} \, \mathrm{J} = \frac{1.12 \times 10^{-18}}{1.6 \times 10^{-19}} = 7.01 \, \mathrm{eV}
\end{aligned}
\]

电子的有效质量:
\[
\begin{aligned}
m_{\mathrm{e}}^{*} = \frac{\hbar^{2}}{\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} E(k)}{\mathrm{d} k^{2}}} = \frac{\hbar^{2}}{\left(-\frac{6 \hbar^{2}}{m}\right)} = -\frac{m}{6} = -\frac{9.11 \times 10^{-31}}{6} = -1.52 \times 10^{-31} \, \mathrm{kg}
\end{aligned}
\]
空穴的有效质量:
\[
m_{\mathrm{h}}^{*} = -m_{\mathrm{e}}^{*} = 1.52 \times 10^{-31} \, \mathrm{kg} = 0.17 m_{0}
\]

由于 \(\boldsymbol{q}_{3} = 2.22 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i} + 0.92 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{j}\) 超出了第一布里渊区的范围 \(1.57 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1}\)，我们采用周期性处理：

选择倒格矢量 \(\boldsymbol{G}_{h} = -\boldsymbol{b}_{1} = -3.14 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i}\)，得

\[
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{q}_{3} & =\boldsymbol{q}_{1}+\boldsymbol{q}_{2}+\boldsymbol{G}_{h}=2.22 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i}+0.92 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{j}-3.14 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i} \\
& =-0.92 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i}+0.92 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{j} \\
& =-\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2} \times 1.3 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i}+\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2} \times 1.3 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{j}
\end{aligned}
\]

调整后声子波矢位于 \([\overline{1}, 1,0]\) 方向，其大小仍为 \(1.3 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1}\)，处于第一布里渊区内。

\[
\begin{aligned}
P_{R} \Psi_{k}^{x}(\boldsymbol{r}) &= \Psi_{k}^{x}\left(\boldsymbol{r}^{\prime}\right) \\
&= c \sum_{n} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k_{0} X_{n}} \phi_{p x}\left(x^{\prime}-X_{n}, y^{\prime}-Y_{n}, z^{\prime}-Z_{n}\right) \\
&= c \sum_{n} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k_{0} X_{n}} \phi_{p x}\left(y-X_{n}, -x-Y_{n}, z-Z_{n}\right) \\
&= c \sum_{n} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k_{0} X_{n}} \left(y-X_{n}\right) f\left(\sqrt{\left(y-X_{n}\right)^{2}+\left(-x-Y_{n}\right)^{2}+\left(z-Z_{n}\right)^{2}}\right) \\
&= c \sum_{n} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} k_{0} X_{n}} \left(y-X_{n}\right) f\left(\sqrt{\left(x+Y_{n}\right)^{2}+\left(y-X_{n}\right)^{2}+\left(z-Z_{n}\right)^{2}}\right)
\end{aligned}
\]

\[
\begin{aligned}
&= c \sum_{n^{\prime}} \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \boldsymbol{r}^{\prime} \cdot \boldsymbol{R}_{n^{\prime}}} \phi_{p y}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{n^{\prime}}\right) \\
&= \Psi_{k}^{y}(\boldsymbol{r})
\end{aligned}
\]

其中：

\[
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime} &= \left(0, k_{0}, 0\right) \\
\boldsymbol{R}_{n^{\prime}} &= -Y_{n} \boldsymbol{i} + X_{n} \boldsymbol{j} + Z_{n} \boldsymbol{k}
\end{aligned}
\]

所以变换结果仍是一个布洛赫波，但波矢变为 \(\boldsymbol{k}^{\prime}=\left(0, k_{0}, 0\right)\)，即是 \(y\) 方向的布洛赫波。

假设硼取替位式位置，按照如下公式计算晶体密度：

\[
\begin{aligned}
\rho_{\mathrm{s}}^{n} & =\frac{797488 \times \frac{28.086 \times 10^{-3}}{6.022 \times 10^{23}}+2512 \times \frac{10.811 \times 10^{-3}}{6.022 \times 10^{23}}}{1 \times 10^{5} \times\left(5.4249 \times 10^{-10}\right)^{3}} \\
& =\frac{797488 \times 28.086 \times 10^{-3}+2512 \times 10.811 \times 10^{-3}}{1 \times 10^{5} \times\left(5.4249 \times 10^{-10}\right)^{3} \times 6.022 \times 10^{23}} \\
& =\frac{22398.24797+27.157}{159.6523116 \times 6.022 \times 10^{-2}} = 2.33251 \times 10^{3} \mathrm{~kg} \cdot \mathrm{m}^{-3}
\end{aligned}
\]

假设硼取填隙式位置，按照如下公式计算晶胞整体的密度：

\[
\begin{aligned}
\rho_{i}^{*} & =\frac{M}{V} \\
& =\frac{8 \times 10^{5} \times \frac{28.086 \times 10^{-3}}{6.022 \times 10^{23}}+2512 \times \frac{10.811 \times 10^{-3}}{6.022 \times 10^{23}}}{1 \times 10^{5} \times\left(5.4249 \times 10^{-10}\right)^{3}} \\
& =\frac{8 \times 10^{5} \times 28.086 \times 10^{-3}+2512 \times 10.811 \times 10^{-3}}{10^{5} \times\left(5.4249 \times 10^{-10}\right)^{3} \times 6.022 \times 10^{23}}
\end{aligned}
\]

计算得到：\(\rho_{i}^{*} = 2.33985 \times 10^{3} \mathrm{~kg} \cdot \mathrm{m}^{-3}\)。

先应用分部积分求 \(I_{1}\)

\[
\begin{aligned}
I_{1} & =-\frac{a_{0}}{2}\left[\left.\left(\sin G r \mathrm{e}^{-\frac{2 r}{a_{0}}}\right)\right|_{0}^{\infty}-\int_{0}^{\infty} G \cos G r \mathrm{e}^{-\frac{2 r}{a_{0}}} \mathrm{d} r\right] \\
& =\frac{G a_{0}}{2} \int_{0}^{\infty} \cos G r \mathrm{e}^{-\frac{2 r}{a_{0}}} \mathrm{d} r=-\frac{G a_{0}^{2}}{4}\left[\left.\left(\cos G r \mathrm{e}^{-\frac{2 r}{a_{0}}}\right)\right|_{0}^{\infty}+\int_{0}^{\infty} G \sin G r \mathrm{e}^{-\frac{2 r}{a_{0}}} \mathrm{d} r\right] \\
& =\frac{G a_{0}^{2}}{4}-\frac{G^{2} a_{0}^{2}}{4} I_{1}
\end{aligned}
\]

移项求得

\[
I_{1}=\frac{G a_{0}^{2}}{4+a_{0}^{2} G^{2}}
\]

类似计算, 求出

\[
I_{2}=\frac{2 a_{0}}{4+a_{0}^{2} G^{2}}
\]

极值条件:
\[
\frac{\mathrm{d} E(k)}{\mathrm{d} k} = -\frac{6 \hbar^{2}}{m} k = 0
\]
晶体满带顶在 \(k=0\)，满带顶电子能量:
\[
\begin{aligned}
E(k=0) &= \frac{\hbar^{2} k_{1}^{2}}{6 m} = \frac{\left(1.055 \times 10^{-34}\right)^{2} \times \left(3.98 \times 10^{8}\right)^{2}}{6 \times 9.11 \times 10^{-31}} \\
&= 3.195 \times 10^{-22} \, \mathrm{J} = 1.994 \times 10^{-3} \, \mathrm{eV}
\end{aligned}
\]
\(k_{1}\) 处出现空穴的能量:
\[
\begin{aligned}
E_{\mathrm{h}} &= -E\left(k_{1}\right) = -\left(\frac{\hbar^{2} k_{1}^{2}}{6 m} - \frac{3 \hbar^{2} k_{1}^{2}}{m}\right) = \frac{17 \hbar^{2} k_{1}^{2}}{6 m} \\
&= \frac{17 \times \left(1.055 \times 10^{-34}\right)^{2} \times \left(3.98 \times 10^{8}\right)^{2}}{6 \times 9.11 \times 10^{-31}} \\
&= 5.489 \times 10^{-21} \, \mathrm{J} = 0.034 \, \mathrm{eV}
\end{aligned}
\]

（2）先求出一个原子与周围最近邻 6 个原子的平均相互作用能 \(u\)。由于假设金属原子 \(A, B\) 是随机无规的分布在各个位置上，所以平均来说，二元合金每一格点上都有 \(\frac{N_{A}}{N}\) 比率的 \(A\) 原子和 \(\frac{N_{B}}{N}\) 比率的 \(B\) 原子作为它的最近邻，而原子 \(A\) 和 \(B\) 本身在某一格点上出现比率也分别是 \(\frac{N_{A}}{N}\) 和 \(\frac{N_{B}}{N}\)。故原子与最近邻原子平均相互作用能
\[
\begin{aligned}
u & =6\left[(-J) \frac{N_{A}}{N}+J \frac{N_{B}}{N}\right] \frac{N_{A}}{N}+6\left[(-J) \frac{N_{B}}{N}+J \frac{N_{A}}{N}\right] \frac{N_{B}}{N} \\
& =6\left[(-J) \frac{N_{A}^{2}+N_{B}^{2}}{N^{2}}+J \frac{2 N_{A} N_{B}}{N^{2}}\right]=-\frac{6 J}{N^{2}}\left(N_{A}-N_{B}\right)^{2}
\end{aligned}
\]
这样，由 \(N_{A}\) 个金属原子 \(A\) 和 \(N_{B}\) 个金属原子 \(B\) 组成的二元合金总的相互作用能
\[
U=\frac{N}{2} u=-\frac{3 J}{N}\left(N_{A}-N_{B}\right)^{2}=-3 N J x^{2}
\]

银的电子浓度 \(n = \frac{10.5}{107.87} \times 6.022 \times 10^{23} = 5.86 \times 10^{22} \ \mathrm{cm}^{-3}\)

费米能 \(E_{\mathrm{F}}\) 和费米温度 \(T_{\mathrm{F}}\)

\[
\begin{aligned}
E_{\mathrm{F}} & = \frac{\hbar^{2}}{2 m}\left(3 \pi^{2} n\right)^{\frac{2}{3}} = \frac{\left(1.05 \times 10^{-34}\right)^{2}}{2 \times 9.1 \times 10^{-31}} \times \left(3 \times 3.14^{2} \times 5.86 \times 10^{22}\right)^{\frac{2}{3}} \\
& = 8.747 \times 10^{-19} \ \mathrm{J} = 5.46 \ \mathrm{eV} \\
T_{\mathrm{F}} & = \frac{E_{\mathrm{F}}}{k_{\mathrm{B}}} = \frac{5.46 \ \mathrm{eV}}{8.617 \times 10^{-5} \ \mathrm{eV/K}} = 6.34 \times 10^{4} \ \mathrm{K}
\end{aligned}
\]

自由电子气模型中，费米球大小决定于金属中电子密度，其费米波矢

\[
k_{\mathrm{F}} = \left(3 n \pi^{2}\right)^{\frac{1}{3}}
\]

钾金属为体心立方结构，体积为 \(a^3\)，晶胞中含有 2 个电子，\(n = \frac{2}{a^3}\)，则

\[
\begin{aligned}
k_{\mathrm{F}} & = \left(3 \mathrm{n} \pi^{2}\right)^{\frac{1}{3}} = \left(3 \times \frac{2}{a^{3}} \pi^{2}\right)^{\frac{1}{3}} = \left(\frac{6\pi^{2}}{a^3}\right)^{\frac{1}{3}} \\
& = 1.240 \times \frac{3.14}{5.333 \times 10^{-10}} = 7.31 \times 10^{9} \ (\mathrm{m}^{-1})
\end{aligned}
\]

又

\[
E_{\mathrm{F}}^{0} = \frac{\hbar^{2} k_{\mathrm{F}}^{2}}{2 m^{*}} = k_{\mathrm{B}} T_{\mathrm{F}}
\]

故

\[
\begin{aligned}
m^{*} & = \frac{\hbar^{2} k_{\mathrm{F}}^{2}}{2 k_{\mathrm{B}} T_{\mathrm{F}}} = \frac{\left(1.055 \times 10^{-34}\right)^{2} \times \left(7.31 \times 10^{9}\right)^{2}}{2 \times 1.38 \times 10^{-23} \times 1.97 \times 10^{4}} \\
& = 1.0939 \times 10^{-30} = 1.2 m_{0}
\end{aligned}
\]

式中 \(m_{0}\) 为电子静止质量。

设声子波长为 \(\lambda^{\prime}\)

\[
\frac{1}{\lambda^{\prime}}=|\boldsymbol{q}|=2\left|\boldsymbol{k}_{0}\right| \sin \frac{\theta}{2}=2 \frac{1}{\lambda_{0}} \sin \frac{\theta}{2}
\]

式中 \(\lambda_{0}\) 是入射光波长，相应声子角频率 \(\omega^{\prime}\) 为

\[
\omega^{\prime}=2 \pi f^{\prime}=\frac{2 \pi}{\lambda^{\prime}} v=4 \pi v \sin \frac{\theta}{2} \frac{1}{\lambda_{0}}
\]

同理，波矢为 \(\boldsymbol{k}_{0}\) 和 \(\boldsymbol{k}\) 的光子分别相应的角频率

\[
\begin{aligned}
\omega_{0} & =2 \pi f_{0}=\frac{2 \pi}{\lambda_{0}} \frac{c}{n} \\
\omega & =2 \pi f=\frac{2 \pi}{\lambda} \frac{c}{n}
\end{aligned}
\]

光子与声子相互作用遵循能量守恒定律，

\[
\hbar \omega-\hbar \omega_{0}= \pm \hbar \omega^{\prime}
\]

将 (1)、(2) 和 (3) 式代入上式

\[
\begin{gathered}
\hbar \frac{2 \pi}{\lambda} \frac{c}{n}-\hbar \frac{2 \pi}{\lambda_{0}} \frac{c}{n}= \pm \hbar \cdot 4 \pi v \sin \frac{\theta}{2} \frac{1}{\lambda_{0}} \\
\frac{1}{\lambda}-\frac{1}{\lambda_{0}}= \pm \frac{2 n v}{c} \frac{1}{\lambda_{0}} \sin \frac{\theta}{2}
\end{gathered}
\]

得出

\[
\lambda-\lambda_{0}= \pm \frac{2 n v}{c} \lambda \sin \frac{\theta}{2}
\]

当两个声子相互作用而形成第三个声子时，波矢守恒，即相互作用前后声子总波矢相等，所以第三个声子波矢

\[
\begin{aligned}
\boldsymbol{q}_{3} & =\boldsymbol{q}_{1}+\boldsymbol{q}_{2} \\
& =1.3 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i}+0.92 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i}+0.92 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{j} \\
& =2.22 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{i}+0.92 \times 10^{10} \, \text{m}^{-1} \, \boldsymbol{j}
\end{aligned}
\]

这意味着合成波矢落在第一布里渊区之外，需要通过空间周期性来调整。

把 \(\rho=3.79 \times 10^{-11} \, \text{m}=0.379 \, \text{Å}\) 代入

\[
\begin{aligned}
\lambda &= \frac{\rho M e^{2}}{4 \pi \varepsilon_{0} r_{0}^{2}} e^{\frac{r_{0}}{\rho}} \\
&= \frac{3.79 \times 10^{-11} \times 1.7476 \times \left(1.602 \times 10^{-19}\right)^{2}}{4 \times 3.1416 \times 8.85 \times 10^{-12} \times \left(3.29 \times 10^{-10}\right)^{2}} e^{\frac{3.29 \times 10^{-10}}{3.79 \times 10^{-11}}} \\
&= 8.315 \times 10^{-16} \, \text{J}
\end{aligned}
\]

由于恢复力减少正比于空位浓度，故晶体中存在 \(n\) 浓度空位时，其恢复力系数为

\[
\begin{aligned}
& c_{1}=c_{1}^{0}(1-B n), \\
& c_{2}=c_{2}^{0}(1-B n)
\end{aligned}
\]

其中 \(c_{1}^{0}, c_{2}^{0}\) 分别为完整晶体时恢复力常数，\(B\) 是比例常数，代入 (2) 式，声速为

\[
\begin{aligned}
v_{s} & =\frac{a}{2} \sqrt{\frac{\left(c_{1}^{0}\right)^{2}(1-B n)^{2} \sin ^{2}\left(q_{1} a\right)+\left(c_{2}^{0}\right)^{2}(1-B n)^{2} \sin ^{2}\left(q_{2} a\right)}{m c_{1}^{0}(1-B n)\left[1-\cos \left(q_{1} a\right)\right]+m c_{2}^{0}(1-B n)\left[1-\cos \left(q_{2} a\right)\right]}} \\
& \propto \sqrt{1-B n} \propto \sqrt{1-B^{\prime} \exp \left(-\frac{\varepsilon}{k_{B} T}\right)}
\end{aligned}
\]

上公式推导应用 \(n \propto \mathrm{e}^{-\frac{\varepsilon}{k_{B} T}}\)。

空穴动量:
\[
\begin{aligned}
P_{\mathrm{h}} &= \hbar k_{\mathrm{h}} = -1.055 \times 10^{-34} \times 3.98 \times 10^{8} = -4.20 \times 10^{-26} \, \mathrm{Ns} \\
&= m_{\mathrm{h}}^{*} v_{\mathrm{h}} = 1.52 \times 10^{-31} \times (-2.77) \times 10^{5} = -4.20 \times 10^{-26} \, \mathrm{Ns}
\end{aligned}
\]

银的电子浓度 \(n = \frac{10.5}{107.87} \times 6.022 \times 10^{23} = 5.86 \times 10^{22} \ \mathrm{cm}^{-3}\)

费米速度 \(v_{\mathrm{F}} = 1.38 \times 10^{8} \ \mathrm{cm/s}\)（由前一步得到）

金属自由电子论

\[
\sigma = \frac{1}{\rho} = \frac{n e^{2} \tau}{m}
\]

则

\[
\tau = \frac{1}{\rho} \cdot \frac{m}{n e^{2}}
\]

在 295 K

\[
\begin{aligned}
\tau & = \frac{1}{1.61 \times 10^{-6}} \cdot \frac{9.1 \times 10^{-31}}{5.86 \times 10^{22} \times \left(1.6 \times 10^{-19}\right)^{2}} \\
& = 3.77 \times 10^{-14} \ \mathrm{s} \\
\bar{\lambda} & = v_{\mathrm{F}} \tau = 1.38 \times 10^{8} \ \mathrm{cm/s} \times 3.77 \times 10^{-14} \ \mathrm{s} = 5.2 \times 10^{-6} \ \mathrm{cm} = 520 \ \mathrm{\angstrom}
\end{aligned}
\]

同理 20 K 下

\[
\begin{aligned}
\tau & = 1.596 \times 10^{-12} \ \mathrm{s} \\
\bar{\lambda} & = 1.38 \times 10^{8} \ \mathrm{cm/s} \times 1.596 \times 10^{-12} \ \mathrm{s} = 2.20 \times 10^{-4} \ \mathrm{cm} = 2.2 \times 10^{4} \ \mathrm{\angstrom}
\end{aligned}
\]

计算每离子对间相互作用能

\[
\begin{aligned}
E_b & = -\frac{M e^2}{4 \pi \varepsilon_0 r_0} \left( 1 - \frac{1}{n} \right) \\
& = -\frac{1.7476 \times \left(1.6 \times 10^{-19}\right)^2}{4 \times 3.1416 \times 8.85 \times 10^{-12} \times 2.82 \times 10^{-10}} \times \left( 1 - \frac{1}{7.8} \right) \\
& = -1.24 \times 10^{-18} \, \mathrm{J}
\end{aligned}
\]

与实验 \(-1.27 \times 10^{-18} \, \mathrm{J}\) 相当接近。

满带 \(k_{1}\) 处电子速度:
\[
\begin{aligned}
v_{\mathrm{e}} &= \left.\frac{1}{\hbar} \frac{\mathrm{d} E}{\mathrm{d} k}\right|_{k=k_{1}} = \frac{1}{\hbar}\left(-1\right) \frac{3 \hbar^{2}}{m} \times 2 k_{1} \\
&= -\frac{6 \hbar k_{1}}{m} = -\frac{6 \times 1.055 \times 10^{-34} \times 3.98 \times 10^{8}}{9.11 \times 10^{-31}} \\
&= -2.77 \times 10^{5} \, \mathrm{m/s}
\end{aligned}
\]
空穴的速度:
\[
v_{\mathrm{h}} = v_{\mathrm{e}} = -2.77 \times 10^{5} \, \mathrm{m/s}
\]

\[
\frac{1}{m^{*}} = \frac{1}{\hbar^{2}} \nabla_{k} \nabla_{k} E = \left(\begin{array}{cc}
\frac{1}{\hbar^{2}} \frac{\partial^{2} E}{\partial k_{x}^{2}} & \frac{1}{\hbar^{2}} \frac{\partial^{2} E}{\partial k_{x} \partial k_{y}} \\
\frac{1}{\hbar^{2}} \frac{\partial^{2} E}{\partial k_{y} \partial k_{x}} & \frac{1}{\hbar^{2}} \frac{\partial^{2} E}{\partial k_{y}^{2}}
\end{array}\right) = \frac{2J}{\hbar^{2}}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
a^{2} \cos k_{x} a & 0 \\
0 & b^{2} \cos k_{y} b
\end{array}\right)
\]

带底电子有效质量，代入 \(k_{x} = 0, k_{y} = 0\)

\[
\frac{1}{m^{*}} = \frac{2J}{\hbar^{2}}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
a^{2} & 0 \\
0 & b^{2}
\end{array}\right)
\]

带顶电子有效质量，代入 \(k_{x} = \frac{\pi}{a}, k_{y} = \frac{\pi}{b}\)

\[
\frac{1}{m^{*}} = \frac{2J}{\hbar^{2}}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
-a^{2} & 0 \\
0 & -b^{2}
\end{array}\right)
\]

则能带顶空穴有效质量

\[
\frac{1}{m_{h}^{*}} = \frac{2J}{\hbar^{2}}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
a^{2} & 0 \\
0 & b^{2}
\end{array}\right)
\]

设二维密排结构面积为 \(S\) ，原子数为 \(N\) ，每个原子贡献一个自由电子，有

\[
\begin{gathered}
2 \cdot \frac{S}{(2 \pi)^{2}} \cdot \pi k_{\mathrm{F}}^{2}=N \\
k_{\mathrm{F}}^{2}=2 \pi \frac{N}{S}
\end{gathered}
\]

\(\frac{N}{S}\) 为单位面积的原子数，可以计算如下，取某一正三角形，其边长为 \(a\) ，三个夹角均等于 \(60^{\circ}\) ，故它的面积为

\[
\frac{1}{2} \times a \times a \times \sin 60^{\circ}=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{4} a^{2}
\]

但正三角形 3 个角顶的每一个原子只有 \(\frac{1}{6}\) 原子属于该正三角形，故一个正三角形仅含 \(\frac{1}{2}\) 个原子

\[
\frac{N}{S}=\frac{\frac{1}{2}}{\frac{\sqrt{3}}{4} a^{2}}=\frac{2}{\sqrt{3} a^{2}}
\]

故费米波矢 \(k_{\mathrm{F}}^{2}=2 \pi \cdot \frac{2}{\sqrt{3} a^{2}}\) ，即

\[
k_{\mathrm{F}}=\frac{2}{a}\left(\frac{\pi}{\sqrt{3}}\right)^{\frac{1}{2}}
\]

answers:
\[
\boxed{q = n \frac{2 \pi}{a}, V_{0} = -\frac{2 A}{a}, V_{n} = -\frac{2 A}{a} \cos \left(n \frac{\pi b}{a}\right)}
\]

solution:
晶体中声速为

\[
v_{g}=\nabla_{q} \omega=\frac{\partial \omega}{\partial q_{1}} \boldsymbol{i}+\frac{\partial \omega}{\partial q_{2}} \boldsymbol{j}
\]

式中 \(\boldsymbol{i}, \boldsymbol{j}\) 分别为 \(x, y\) 方向单位矢量，代入色散关系得

\[
\boldsymbol{v}_{g}=\frac{2}{a} \frac{c_{1} \sin \left(q_{1} a\right) \boldsymbol{i}+c_{2} \sin \left(q_{2} a\right) \boldsymbol{j}}{\sqrt{m c_{1}\left[1-\cos \left(q_{1} a\right)\right]+m c_{2}\left[1-\cos \left(q_{2} a\right)\right]}}
\]

所以

\[
\begin{aligned}
v_{s}=\left|v_{g}\right| & =\frac{a}{2} \sqrt{\frac{c_{1}^{2} \sin ^{2}\left(q_{1} a\right)+c_{2}^{2} \sin ^{2}\left(q_{2} a\right)}{m c_{1}\left[1-\cos \left(q_{1} a\right)\right]+m c_{2}\left[1-\cos \left(q_{2} a\right)\right]}} \\
& =\frac{a}{m \omega} \sqrt{c_{1}^{2} \sin ^{2}\left(q_{1} a\right)+c_{2}^{2} \sin ^{2}\left(q_{2} a\right)}
\end{aligned}
\]

推导中利用 \(m \omega^{2}=2 c_{1}\left[1-\cos \left(q_{1} a\right)\right]+2 c_{2}\left[1-\cos \left(q_{2} a\right)\right]\)。

（2）电子周期势场 \(V(x)\) 可写成 \(V(x)=V_{0}+\Delta V(x)\) ，周期势场 \(V(x)\) 傅里叶展开系数 \(V_{n}\) 为  

\[  
\begin{aligned}  
& V_{n}=\frac{1}{a} \int_{-b}^{b} \frac{1}{2} m \omega^{2}\left(b^{2}-x^{2}\right) \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} n \frac{2 \pi}{a} x} \mathrm{~d} x \\  
& =\frac{m \omega^{2}}{2 a} \int_{-b}^{b} b^{2} \mathrm{e}^{- \mathrm{i} \frac{2 \pi}{a} x} \mathrm{~d} x-\frac{m \omega^{2}}{2 a} \int_{-b}^{b} x^{2} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{2 \pi}{a} x} \mathrm{~d} x  
\end{aligned}  
\]  

\[  
\begin{aligned}  
& =-\frac{m \omega^{2} b^{2}}{4 n \pi \mathrm{i}}\left[\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2}}-\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2}}\right]+\frac{m \omega^{2} b^{2}}{4 n \pi \mathrm{i}}\left[\mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2}}-\mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2}}\right]-\frac{m \omega^{2}}{2 n \pi \mathrm{i}} \int_{-b}^{b} x \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2 b} x} \mathrm{~d} x  
\end{aligned}  
\]  

\[  
= \frac{m\omega^2 b}{8} \cdot \frac{2b}{-i n \pi} e^{-i \frac{n \pi}{2b} x} \bigg|_{-b}^b   
- \frac{m \omega^2}{8b} \cdot \frac{1}{-i \frac{n \pi}{2b}} x^2 e^{-i \frac{n \pi}{2b} x} \bigg|_{-b}^b   
+ \frac{m \omega^2}{4b} \cdot \frac{1}{-i \frac{n \pi}{2b}} \int_{-b}^b x e^{-i \frac{n \pi}{2b} x} \, dx  
\]  

所以  

\[  
\begin{aligned}  
V_{n} & =-\frac{m \omega^{2}}{2 n \pi \mathrm{i}} \int_{-b}^{b} x \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2 b} x} \mathrm{~d} x \\  
& =-\frac{m \omega^{2}}{2 n \pi \mathrm{i}}\left\{\left.\left[\frac{2 b}{-\mathrm{i} n \pi} x \cdot \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{2 \pi x}{a}}\right]\right|_{-b} ^{b}+\frac{2 b}{\mathrm{i} n \pi} \int_{-b}^{b} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{n x}{2 b^{2}}} \mathrm{~d} x\right\}  
\end{aligned}  
\]  

\[  
\begin{aligned}  
& =-\frac{m \omega^{2} b}{n^{2} \pi^{2}}\left[b \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2}}+b \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2}}\right]+\left.\frac{m \omega^{2} b}{n^{2} \pi^{2}} \cdot \frac{2 b}{-\mathrm{i} n \pi} \mathrm{e}^{-\mathrm{i} \frac{n \pi}{2 b^{2}}}\right|_{-b} ^{b} \\  
& =-\frac{2 m \omega^{2} b^{2}}{n^{2} \pi^{2}} \cos \frac{n \pi}{2}+\frac{4 m \omega^{2} b^{2}}{n^{3} \pi^{3}} \sin \frac{n \pi}{2}  
\end{aligned}  
\]  

故 \(n=1\) ，第一禁带宽度为  

\[  
E_{g 1}=2\left|V_{1}\right|=\frac{8 m \omega^{2} b^{2}}{\pi^{3}}  
\]  

\(n=2\) ，第二禁带宽度为  

\[  
E_{g 2}=2\left|V_{2}\right|=\frac{m \omega^{2} b^{2}}{\pi^{2}}  
\]
